  m_text: "Resolve Map1 Incident\r\nsuburban_map_01  |  2026-04-27 21:45\r\nBest
    record for this level\r\n\r\nCall Phase\r\nScore: 92/112\r\nCall Time: 00:27
    / Target 01:30\r\nSeverity: CAO / Expected CAO\r\nFollow-up: T\u1ED1t (3 optimal,
    2 acceptable, 0 poor)\r\nFeedback:\r\n- M\u1EE9c \u0111\u1ED9 \u0111\xE1nh gi\xE1
    th\u1EA5p h\u01A1n m\u1EE9c k\u1EF3 v\u1ECDng.\r\n- Address, occupant risk, and
    caller safety were confirmed.\r\n- C\xE1c chi ti\u1EBFt s\u1EF1 c\u1ED1 quan
    tr\u1ECDng kh\u1EDBp t\u1ED1t v\u1EDBi k\u1ECBch b\u1EA3n.\r\n- B\xE1o c\xE1o
    \u0111\xE3 s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng \u0111\u1EC3 n\u1ED9p.\r\n- B\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 \u01B0u
    ti\xEAn c\xE1c c\xE2u h\u1ECFi b\u1ED5 sung kh\xE1 h\u1EE3p l\xFD.\r\n- T\u1ED1c
    \u0111\u1ED9 x\u1EED l\xFD cu\u1ED9c g\u1ECDi hi\u1EC7u qu\u1EA3 cho k\u1ECBch
    b\u1EA3n n\xE0y.\r\n\r\nOnsite Phase\r\nScore: 30/30  |  Rank: S\r\nTime: 00:52\r\nFires:
